    "narrative": "On February [XXX], 2025 at 6:11 AM PT a Waymo Autonomous Vehicle (\"Waymo AV\") operating in San Francisco was in a collision involving debris on [XXX] near [XXX]. \nThe Waymo AV was traveling northbound in the leftmost lane on [XXX] when the front passenger side tire of the Waymo AV made contact with a piece of debris that was in the roadway, causing the Waymo AV to slow to a stop. The passenger car traveling directly behind the Waymo AV also slowed to a stop, causing a second passenger car traveling behind the first passenger car to also slow. While the second passenger car was slowing, a third passenger car traveling behind the second passenger car began to merge into the center lane and the front driver side of the third passenger car made contact with the rear passenger side of the second passenger car. At the time of the impact, the Waymo AV's Level 4 ADS was engaged in autonomous mode. The second and third passenger cars sustained damage. \nWaymo is reporting this crash under Request No. 2 of Standing General Order 2021-01. Waymo may supplement or correct its reporting with additional information as it may become available.",
