    "narrative": "On August [XXX], 2025 at 1:50 PM PT a Waymo Autonomous Vehicle (\"Waymo AV\") operating in San Francisco, California was in a collision involving a motorcycle on [XXX] at [XXX]. \nThe Waymo AV was traveling southbound in the left lane on [XXX] when it slowed to a stop for a queue of traffic for a red light at the intersection with [XXX]. A motorcycle traveling southbound in the left lane on [XXX] began passing the Waymo AV on the right side, maneuvering between the Waymo AV and a passenger car stopped in the right lane. As the motorcycle passed between the Waymo AV and the stationary passenger car, a passenger in the passenger car opened the rear left side door and the motorcycle made contact with the open rear left side door of the passenger car. As the motorcycle fell to the left, the motorcycle made contact with the right side of the stationary Waymo AV. At the time of the impact, the Waymo AV's Level 4 ADS was engaged in autonomous mode. The Waymo AV and the passenger car sustained damage. The motorcyclist alleged a minor injury.\nWaymo is reporting this crash under Request No. 2. Waymo may supplement or correct its reporting with additional information as it may become available.",
