    "narrative": "On October [XXX], 2025 at 8:53 AM PT a Waymo Autonomous Vehicle (\"Waymo AV\") operating in Mountain View, California was in a collision involving a pickup truck on [XXX] at [XXX]. \nThe Waymo AV was stopped facing southeast in the rightmost lane on [XXX] in a queue of traffic for a red light at the intersection at [XXX]. After the traffic light turned green, the Waymo AV proceeded a short distance forward before coming to a stop to yield to the stationary SUV directly in front of the Waymo AV. As the Waymo AV came to a stop, a pickup truck that was initially stopped directly behind the Waymo AV began to proceed forward. The Waymo AV then began to proceed forward again after the SUV ahead proceeded forward, and the front of the pickup truck then made contact with the rear of the Waymo AV.  At the time of the impact, the Waymo AV's Level 4 ADS was engaged in autonomous mode. Both vehicles sustained damage.\n\nWaymo is reporting this crash under Request No. 1 of Standing General Order 2021-01 because a vehicle involved was towed away. Waymo may supplement or correct its reporting with additional information as it may become available.",
