    "narrative": "On November [XXX], 2025 at 10:15 PM PT a Waymo Autonomous Vehicle (\"Waymo AV\") operating in Los Angeles, California was in a collision involving an SUV on [XXX] at [XXX].\nThe Waymo AV was stopped facing north in the left turn lane on [XXX] in a queue of traffic for a red light at the intersection with [XXX]. After the light turned green and traffic ahead advanced, the Waymo AV proceeded forward before coming to a stop partially in the marked crosswalk with hazard lights activated. An SUV that was initially stopped directly behind the Waymo AV proceeded forward and came to a stop directly behind the stationary Waymo AV. While the Waymo AV and the SUV were stopped, a pickup truck that was initially stopped directly behind the SUV approached the stopped SUV from behind and the front of the pickup truck made contact with the rear of the stationary SUV. The front of the SUV then made contact with the rear of the stationary Waymo AV. At the time of the impact, the Waymo AV's Level 4 ADS was engaged in autonomous mode. All three vehicles sustained damage. The passenger in the Waymo AV alleged minor injury.\n\nWaymo is reporting this crash under Request No. 2 of Standing General Order 2021-01. Waymo may supplement or correct its reporting with additional information as it may become available.",
